OL,5,Cafter review
OL,7,FReacting to the report, Health
OL,8,FSecretary Wes Streeting said: "The
OL,9,Ftragedy is ` and I can't imagine, even
OL,10,Fhaving met families on a number of
OL,11,Foccasions now ` I can't imagine the
OL,12,Funbearable brief they are going
OL,13,Fthrough, let alone to contemplate
OL,14,Fgoing through that grief knowing that
OL,15,Fthese deaths were preventable if the
OL,16,FNHS had been there when it should have
OL,17,Fbeen.
