OL,7,F"It is a catalogue of continual
OL,8,Ffailure for years, it's not a one-off
OL,9,Ftragedy this... there are more Valdo
OL,10,FCalocane's out in our community," she
OL,11,Fsaid.
OL,13,F"I said since the beginning of this
OL,14,Fyear it is a case of when it happens
OL,15,Fagain and not if... and it's going to
OL,16,Fcontinue if nothing changes."
OL,18,FShe called the support for the
OL,19,Fvictims' families since Calocane's
OL,20,Fmurders "appalling."
