OL,11,FMr Coates' son James, also spoke of
OL,12,Fthe review into Calocane's care, he
OL,13,Fsaid: "If they'd just done the job a
OL,14,Flittle bit better or properly, maybe
OL,15,FValdo's trajectory, might have been
OL,16,Fput in a different direction.
OL,18,F"Or maybe he might have been inside
OL,19,Fand getting the help he needed before."
