OL,7,FCalocane was diagnosed with
OL,8,Fschizophrenia three years before
OL,9,Flaunching his van and knife attack in
OL,10,FNottingham city centre and had been
OL,11,Fsectioned four times.
OL,13,FOne of the failures listed by
OL,14,FTuesday's report highlights that risk
OL,15,Fassessments didn't make the danger he
OL,16,Fposed clear enough.
OL,18,FThe CQC report also questioned how
OL,19,Fwell the trust engaged with Calocane's
OL,20,Ffamily - as it found information from
OL,21,Fthem was not consistently acted upon.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/15
