OL,4,Cavoidable', say victims' families
OL,5,Cafter review
OL,7,FThe parents of Grace O'Malley Kumar,
OL,8,Falso killed in the attack, believe
OL,9,Ftragedy could have been averted if
OL,10,FCalocane's care was properly delivered.
OL,12,F"Each time he was sectioned, his
OL,13,Ftreatment didn't change or people can
OL,14,Fbe bothered to change his treatment,"
OL,15,Fsaid Grace's father, Dr Sanjoy Kumar.
OL,17,F"I'm more than convinced that this was
OL,18,Fwholly avoidable if this person had
OL,19,Fbeen treated with any form of
OL,20,Fresponsibility whatsoever."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/15
