OL,7,FGrace's mother, Dr Sinead O'Malley,
OL,8,Fwants those in charge of his care to
OL,9,Fbe held fully responsible.
OL,11,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,12,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,13,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,14,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,16,FShe said: "We want accountability
OL,17,Fbecause any doctor who fails or is
OL,18,Fnegligent needs to be held accountable
OL,19,Fquite frankly, and we see that there's
OL,20,Fbeen multiple failures in the delivery
OL,21,Fof standard treatment."
