OL,7,FThe CQC said Calocane had "little
OL,8,Funderstanding or acceptance of his
OL,9,Fcondition" which could "have
OL,10,Fsignificantly impaired his ability" to
OL,11,Fweigh up the pros and cons of
OL,12,Fantipsychotic treatment and the risks
OL,13,Fof discontinuing it.
OL,15,FIt would have been possible to treat
OL,16,Fhim under section three of the Mental
OL,17,FHealth Act (MHA) 1983 ` which would
OL,18,Fhave given doctors the power to
OL,19,Fadminister drugs against his will ` on
OL,20,Fhis fourth admission to hospital in
OL,21,FJanuary 2022, the regulator said.
