OL,7,FInstead, he was treated under section
OL,8,Ftwo of the act, which is usually for
OL,9,Fpatients who are not known to mental
OL,10,Fhealth services.
OL,12,FAmong its recommendations, the CQC
OL,13,Fsaid NHFT should review treatment
OL,14,Fplans for people with schizophrenia
OL,15,Fregularly, as well as ensure clinical
OL,16,Fsupervision of decisions to detain
OL,17,Fpeople under sections two and three of
OL,18,Fthe Mental Health Act.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/15
