OL,7,FIt also called for NHS England to
OL,8,Fpublish guidance setting out national
OL,9,Fstandards for care for people with
OL,10,Fcomplex psychosis and paranoid
OL,11,Fschizophrenia in the next 12 months.
OL,13,FA Nottinghamshire Healthcare NHS
OL,14,FFoundation Trust spokesperson said:
OL,15,F"We acknowledge and accept the
OL,16,Fconclusions of this report and have
OL,17,Fsignificantly improved processes and
OL,18,Fstandards since the review was carried
OL,19,Fout."
