OL,7,FClaire Murdoch, national director for
OL,8,Fmental health at NHS England, said:
OL,9,F"The CQC has identified unacceptable
OL,10,Ffailings in the care and treatment
OL,11,Fprovided to Valdo Calocane.
OL,13,F"Nationally, the NHS has already
OL,14,Fstarted work to enact all of the CQC's
OL,15,Frecommendations, with every provider
OL,16,Fof mental health services reviewing
OL,17,Fthe care that people with serious
OL,18,Fmental illness receive."
